# Phase 2: RAG 파이프라인

## Context
Phase 1(MindLang API)에서 HTTP 검색 서버를 완성했으므로,
이제 대규모 문서를 임베딩하여 LLM의 지식 베이스로 활용하는
실전 AI 워크플로우(RAG)를 구현한다.

## RAG 플로우
```
사용자 질문
  → Document Chunking (512토큰/청크, 50토큰 오버랩)
  → Batch Embedding (HybridIndexSystem에 저장)
  → Hybrid Search (Top-5 유사 청크 검색, 0.054ms)
  → Prompt 구성 (Context + Question)
  → LLM 호출 (Claude API)
  → 최종 응답 반환
```

## 재사용할 기존 코드

| 파일 | 재사용 내용 |
|------|------------|
| `src/vectordb/mod.fl` | `insertTextHybrid`, `insertTextsHybrid`, `searchByTextHybrid` |
| `src/vectordb/embedding.fl` | `tokenize`, `computeTFIDF`, `embedText` |
| `src/api/handlers.fl` | `handleSearch` 패턴 (재사용하지 않지만 참고) |
| `src/api/server.fl` | `buildSuccessResponse`, `buildErrorResponse` 패턴 |

## 구현할 파일 (5개)

### 1. `src/rag/chunker.fl` (250줄)
```
struct Chunk
  id: string
  text: string
  docId: string           # 원본 문서 ID
  chunkIndex: number      # 청크 번호
  tokenCount: number      # 토큰 수
  metadata: map<string, string>

struct ChunkConfig
  maxTokens: number       # 기본 512
  overlapTokens: number   # 기본 50 (슬라이딩 윈도우)
  minChunkTokens: number  # 기본 50 (너무 작은 청크 제거)

fn chunkDocument(doc, config) → array<Chunk>
fn chunkByParagraph(text) → array<string>
fn chunkBySentence(text, maxTokens) → array<string>
fn estimateTokenCount(text) → number
fn mergeSmallChunks(chunks, minTokens) → array<Chunk>
fn buildChunkId(docId, chunkIndex) → string
```

### 2. `src/rag/batch.fl` (300줄)
```
struct BatchEmbeddingConfig
  batchSize: number       # 기본 100 (청크/배치)
  parallelBatches: number # 기본 4 (병렬 배치 수)
  maxRetries: number      # 기본 3 (임베딩 재시도)

struct BatchEmbeddingResult
  totalChunks: number
  processedChunks: number
  failedChunks: number
  totalTimeMs: number
  avgTimePerChunk: number

fn embedChunkBatch(chunks, hybridSys, config) → Result<BatchEmbeddingResult, string>
fn embedSingleChunk(chunk, hybridSys) → Result<HybridIndexSystem, string>
fn retryFailedChunks(failed, hybridSys, maxRetries) → array<string>  # 실패 청크 ID
fn reportBatchProgress(current, total) → string
fn estimateBatchTime(chunkCount, avgMs) → string
```

### 3. `src/rag/pipeline.fl` (400줄)
```
struct RagPipeline
  hybridSys: HybridIndexSystem
  chunkConfig: ChunkConfig
  batchConfig: BatchEmbeddingConfig
  llmConfig: LLMConfig
  stats: PipelineStats

struct PipelineStats
  totalDocuments: number
  totalChunks: number
  totalQueries: number
  avgSearchMs: number
  avgLLMMs: number

fn newRagPipeline(hybridSys, llmConfig) → RagPipeline
fn ingestDocument(pipeline, docId, text, metadata) → Result<PipelineStats, string>
fn ingestBatch(pipeline, documents) → Result<PipelineStats, string>
fn query(pipeline, question) → Result<RagResponse, string>
fn buildContext(chunks, maxContextLen) → string
fn buildPrompt(question, context) → string
fn postProcessResponse(llmResp) → string
fn getPipelineStats(pipeline) → PipelineStats
```

### 4. `src/rag/llm_integration.fl` (200줄)
```
struct LLMConfig
  model: string           # "claude-haiku-4-5"
  maxTokens: number       # 기본 1024
  temperature: number     # 기본 0.3
  systemPrompt: string    # RAG 특화 시스템 프롬프트

struct LLMRequest
  model: string
  messages: array<Message>
  maxTokens: number
  temperature: number

struct Message
  role: string            # "user" | "assistant" | "system"
  content: string

struct LLMResponse
  content: string
  inputTokens: number
  outputTokens: number
  model: string
  timeMs: number

struct RagResponse
  answer: string
  sources: array<string>  # 참조된 청크 ID
  confidence: number      # 0.0 ~ 1.0
  searchTimeMs: number
  llmTimeMs: number
  totalTimeMs: number

fn callLLM(config, messages) → Result<LLMResponse, string>
fn buildRagMessages(systemPrompt, question, context) → array<Message>
fn parseRagResponse(llmResp) → RagResponse
fn estimateConfidence(searchResults, question) → number
```

